## ğŸ”— index.md

```markdown
# ğŸš€ Cybersecurity Learning Hub

Welcome to your modular cybersecurity learning kit. This GitHub Pages site integrates:

- Cisco Junior Cybersecurity Analyst Path
- TryHackMe Career Tracks
- EC-Council Essentials & Certifications
- Reading Plans, Badge Tracker, and Sprint Planner

Start with the [Roadmap](./roadmap.md) or jump into a provider-specific path:
- [Cisco Path](./cisco/overview.md)
- [TryHackMe Path](./tryhackme/overview.md)
- [EC-Council Path](./eccouncil/overview.md)
