## ğŸ§­ roadmap.md

```markdown
# ğŸ§­ Cybersecurity Roadmap Overview

| Provider     | Entry-Level Path             | Intermediate Track         | Advanced Track               |
|--------------|------------------------------|-----------------------------|------------------------------|
| Cisco        | CCST Cybersecurity           | CyberOps Associate          | CCNP/CCIE Security           |
| TryHackMe    | Presecurity + Foundations    | SOC / Pentester / Engineer | CPTS Certification           |
| EC-Council   | Essentials Series (EHE, DFE) | CEH / CND / CHFI            | LPT / ECSA / CISA / CISM     |

Use this roadmap to guide your sprint planning and badge tracking.
```

